data.description: Discover the epitome of Southwestern living in this breathtaking 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasting classic New Mexico charm. This home has been meticulously maintained and radiates bright open spaces and invites you to live and entertain friends and family.From the freshly painted Exterior, you'll enter through the courtyard, into the Open Main Living areas. You'll appreciate the beautiful columns, the kiva style fireplace, and the beautiful Custom cabinetry throughout the home. Additional updates include an engineered hardwood floor in the dining area, wood blinds, fresh interior paint, and fresh desert landscaping in the backyard. Many more features that make this home one-of-a-kind! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your home! VA Assumable Rate opportunity.
